title: Reaction to Jalen Ramsey & Marcus Peters trades, Matt Rhule talks building Baylor
itunes:title: Reaction to Jalen Ramsey & Marcus Peters trades, Matt Rhule talks building Baylor
description:
DJ and Bucky are back with a new episode. First, the pair react to the Rams' trade for cornerback Jalen Ramsey (2:13) and the Ravens' trade for Marcus Peters (17:52). Next, DJ and Bucky discuss if this is the final season for Marcus Mariota in Tennessee and the final year for Jameis Winston in Tampa Bay (24:16). After that, the guys talk to Baylor head coach Matt Rhule about the culture of the team and how he's leading the team to an undefeated season so far (33:27). Then, the duo compare two of the top college wide receivers in the nation (53:31). Later, DJ breaks out another edition of "hits & misses" as he looks back at a player he hit on and a player he missed on from the 2015 NFL Draft (1:05:50). To wrap up the show, the pair answer fan questions, which were left in the reviews (1:12:06).
